2011;;Four;;British;;Director: John Langridge;;Director: John LangridgeCast: Martin Compston, Craig Conway, Kierston Wareing, Sean Pertwee;;unknown;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Four_(2011_film);;A jealous husband hires a movie-obsessed detective to kidnap his wife's lover and bring him to a derelict factory to administer some 'rough justice.' Once there, the husband discovers the detective has a revelation of his own. He has kidnapped the husband's wife as well.[1]